所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • client.net,
  • client.startup,
  • client.view,
  • common,
  • server.controller,
  • server.model,
  • server.net

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.controller.Controller
    • client.startup.Main
    • common.MessageSplitter
    • client.view.NonBlockingInterpreter (implements java.lang.Runnable)
    • server.net.PlayerHandler
    • server.model.RockPaperScissor
    • server.net.Server (implements java.lang.Runnable)
    • client.net.ServerConnection (implements java.lang.Runnable)
    • java.lang.Throwable (implements java.io.Serializable)
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • common.MessageException

接口分层结构

  • client.net.CommunicationListener

枚举分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<E> (implements java.lang.Comparable<T>, java.io.Serializable)
      • client.view.Command
      • common.MsgType
